---
// AuthorityStatement.astro
// What Wilfred builds and why it matters to the visitor
---

<section
  class="relative py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden"
  aria-label="Authority Statement"
>
  <!-- Decorative right edge line -->
  <div
    class="absolute right-6 lg:right-12 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-cyber/15 to-transparent"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Left: label column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="sticky top-24">
          <span class="section-label">What I Build</span>
          <div class="mt-3 w-12 h-px bg-gold/40"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9">

        <!-- Lead statement -->
        <h2
          class="font-heading font-700 text-slate-100 mb-8 leading-tight"
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          Enterprise technology leaders hire me when they need
          <span class="text-gradient-gold">transformation that actually ships</span>
          — not a roadmap that expires.
        </h2>

        <!-- Body paragraphs -->
        <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-slate-400" style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          <p>
            I design and build Dark Factories: fully autonomous, AI-orchestrated
            operational pipelines where the system handles every step from task
            intake to artifact delivery. No human operators in the loop. No
            bottlenecks. No sprint theater.
          </p>
          <p>
            My current flagship — <span class="text-slate-200 font-600">The Sovereign Council</span> — is a live
            operational system running thirteen specialized AI agents across
            strategy, venture architecture, legal compliance, financial intelligence,
            and digital build execution. It is not a demo. It is my primary
            operating infrastructure.
          </p>
          <p>
            If your organization is serious about AI transformation — not
            exploration, not pilot programs, not proof-of-concept theater — I
            am the architect who builds the real thing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Capability cards -->
        <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {
            [
              {
                title: "Dark Factory Design",
                desc: "End-to-end autonomous pipeline architecture. Zero human operator touchpoints between spec and delivery.",
                icon: "⬡",
              },
              {
                title: "AI Transformation Advisory",
                desc: "$1,000/hr strategy engagement for CTO, VP Engineering, and Head of AI at F500 and high-growth organizations.",
                icon: "◈",
              },
              {
                title: "Systems Engineering",
                desc: "15+ years principal-level. Azure · Claude · Python · LangFlow · Semantic Kernel. Hands on, not just hands waving.",
                icon: "⬢",
              },
              {
                title: "Speaking & Panels",
                desc: "Available for conferences, keynotes, and panels on autonomous systems, AI architecture, and the future of work.",
                icon: "◉",
              },
            ].map((card) => (
              <div class="gold-border-hover p-6 group">
                <div class="text-gold/60 font-mono text-xl mb-3 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200">
                  {card.icon}
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-600 text-slate-100 text-sm tracking-wide mb-2">
                  {card.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  {card.desc}
                </p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
